{"type":"message","id":"01882418","parentId":"d648a7ff","timestamp":"2026-03-10T03:03:06.070Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The tushare-data skill documentation is quite comprehensive. I need to:\n\n1. First check if the market is open today (March 10, 2026 is a Tuesday)\n2. Get real-time stock data for the watchlist\n3. Apply alert rules\n4. Send notifications if there are alerts\n\nLet me first create a Python script to get the real-time data using tushare. I need to:\n1. Check if today is a trading day and if market is closed\n2. Get real-time data for all stocks in the watchlist\n3. Filter based on alert rules\n4. Send notifications\n\nLet me first check the date and create a script to get the data. The watchlist has these stocks:\n- 601857.SH (中国石油)\n- 601808.SH (中海油服)\n- 600256.SH (广汇能源)\n- 600583.SH (海油工程)\n- 000852.SZ (石化机械)\n- 600547.SH (山东黄金)\n- 601069.SH (西部黄金)\n- 600988.SH (赤峰黄金)\n- 000975.SZ (银泰黄金) - note: in realtime-data.txt it shows as 山金国际\n- 002716.SZ (金贵银业) - note: in realtime-data.txt it shows as 湖南白银\n- 601899.SH (紫金矿业)\n- 9866.HK (蔚来-SW) - HK stock\n- AAPL (苹果) - US stock\n- 920876 (慧为智能) - need to check format\n- 688111.SH (金山办公)\n\nFor the alert rules:\n- General: drop > 3% or rise > 5%\n- 中国石油 (601857.SH): rise > 2% or drop > 1%\n\nLet me create a Python script to fetch real-time data and process it. First, I need to clear the realtime-data.txt file properly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_75b5748028fa4b819641accc","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"\" > ~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773111764743}}
