{"type":"message","id":"11404ac5","parentId":"c71319ba","timestamp":"2026-03-10T03:04:44.235Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The script detected that it's currently lunch break (11:00-13:00). However, looking at the current time (11:01 AM), this is actually just before the lunch break. The A股 market trades from 9:30-11:30 and 13:00-15:00. So at 11:01 AM, the market should still be open (morning session ends at 11:30).\n\nLet me fix the script to correctly handle the time check. The issue is in my time check logic - I'm checking `if 11 <= hour < 13` which would trigger at 11:00, but the market actually closes at 11:30.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f64a61a7892240e78a645d2a","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/get_realtime_data.py","oldText":"    # 下午 3 点后算收盘\n    if hour >= 15:\n        print(\"已收盘 (15:00 后)\")\n        return False\n    # 中午休市时间\n    if 11 <= hour < 13:\n        print(\"中午休市时间\")\n        return False\n    # 早上 9:30 前\n    if hour < 9 or (hour == 9 and minute < 30):\n        print(\"尚未开盘 (9:30 前)\")\n        return False","newText":"    # 下午 3 点后算收盘\n    if hour >= 15:\n        print(\"已收盘 (15:00 后)\")\n        return False\n    # 中午休市时间 (11:30-13:00)\n    if hour > 11 or (hour == 11 and minute >= 30):\n        if hour < 13:\n            print(\"中午休市时间 (11:30-13:00)\")\n            return False\n    elif hour < 9 or (hour == 9 and minute < 30):\n        print(\"尚未开盘 (9:30 前)\")\n        return False"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773111871635}}
