{"type":"message","id":"4c2ed0af","parentId":"2d399b54","timestamp":"2026-03-10T03:05:13.635Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The script is having issues with the realtime_daily interface. It fell back to daily data but then says \"未能获取到实时数据\" (failed to get real-time data). Let me check what's happening with the data fetching and fix the issue. The problem might be that the DataFrame is empty or the formatting function is not working correctly.\n\nLet me debug this by checking what data we're actually getting.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d067f47f252e400f8025350f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock && python3 -c \"\nimport tushare as ts\nimport os\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\ntoken = os.getenv('TUSHARE_TOKEN')\npro = ts.pro_api(token)\n\n# Try to get daily data for a few stocks\nts_codes = '601857.SH,601808.SH,600256.SH'\ntoday = datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\nprint(f'Today: {today}')\n\ndata = pro.query('daily', ts_code=ts_codes, start_date=today, end_date=today)\nprint('Data columns:', data.columns if data is not None else 'None')\nprint('Data:', data)\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773111905412}}
